  11:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** 
  12:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** For now only Normal Mode is supported,
  13:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** Sample and hold mode provides reduced power consumption, but requires a bit more setup.
  14:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  **
